@startuml high-level-lifecycle
title Livespec — High-Level Lifecycle
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam BackgroundColor white
skinparam ArrowColor #111
skinparam ArrowFontColor #111
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam usecase {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam card {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}

rectangle "Initial seed of intent" as SeedIntent
card      "Command:\n/livespec:seed" as SeedCmd
database  "SPECIFICATION/" as Spec

rectangle "Implement\nfrom specification" as ImplementFromSpec #FFFFFF;line.dashed
database  "IMPLEMENTATION\n(repo code, tests, config)" as Impl

rectangle "Observe\nspecification, implementation,\nbehavior, or tooling" as Observe #FFFFFF;line.dashed
usecase   "Does this\nchange a project\nrequirement?" as DecideRequirement

card      "Command:\n/livespec:propose-change\n→ /livespec:revise" as SpecChangeCmds
card      "Command:\n/livespec-implementation:plan\n(freeform `bd create`,\nuser-consented)" as ImplOnlyCmd
database  ".beads/\nissue tracker\n(gap-tied + freeform)" as Beads

card      "Command:\n/livespec-implementation:implement\n(Red→Green; close with audit)" as ImplementCmd

SeedIntent --> SeedCmd
SeedCmd --> Spec
Spec --> ImplementFromSpec
ImplementFromSpec --> Impl
Impl --> Observe
Spec --> Observe
Observe --> DecideRequirement

DecideRequirement -down-> SpecChangeCmds : YES\n(spec gap;\ngap-tied issue)
DecideRequirement -down-> ImplOnlyCmd : NO\n(implementation-only;\nfreeform issue)

SpecChangeCmds --> Beads : gap-tied issue,\nlabel `gap-id:gap-NNNN`
SpecChangeCmds --> Spec : updates spec\n(via revise)
ImplOnlyCmd --> Beads : freeform issue,\nno `gap-id:` label

Beads --> ImplementCmd
ImplementCmd --> Impl
ImplementCmd --> Beads : close\n(--resolution fix\nor freeform)

note right of DecideRequirement : Diagnostic: would `current.json`\nchange after `refresh-gaps`?\nYES → spec lifecycle (left).\nNO  → implementation-only (right).\n(Captured in\nresearch/workflow-processes/\nspec-vs-implementation-line.md.)

note bottom of Spec : Mutated only via\n`/livespec:propose-change` →\n`/livespec:revise`. Direct edits\nforbidden by the spec's own\nself-application rule.

note bottom of Beads : Source of truth: embedded Dolt.\nExport view: `.beads/issues.jsonl`\n(git-tracked, human-readable).
@enduml
